responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "D861E65C453A7F057FA3168682A462AF", "Let your service to the empire begin here. Beside me is the Commission Board. Upon it you will find a number of missions to partake in. Each serves the prosperity of the whole. Choose your service and speak with me again.")
